commit.message: Fix typo for Mega meter F
Include uptime information in Hello message.
Add heartbeat: ping the host every 10s.
docs: Updates for Kegboard Pro Mini.

Fix misplaced cast that was breaking Uno/Mega.

Also a few other warning-related cleanups.

KBPM: Flash RX/TX LEDs in lieu of dedicated flow LEDs.

(Only when serial is disconnected).
Add configuration for KBPM board type.

Clean up Arduino firmware build.

Enables -Werror on first-party code. Removes Magstripe
due to compile errors and lack of use (will add it
back if someone cleans it up).
kegboard-mini: Clean up board labels, no functional changes; bump to v1.0.1.
python: Add convenience methods; add kegboard-info.py
Add support for pulsating chip LED.
Add EEPROM.h to sketch (to satisfy broken Arduino IDE).
